{"id": 1553, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都见过哪些爱的微妙表达？", "description": "你的亲对象、亲朋友以及亲爸亲妈都是怎样清新脱俗地爱你的。（题图来自：June Tate）", "record_count": 4907, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201703061113099p7QRnVPqLyXZ2xG.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-03-11T17:00:44Z", "options": [{"id": 177920, "content": "故意将一些东西落下", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 967857}, {"id": 178176, "content": "老公，洗碗了吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948915}, {"id": 178432, "content": "炒菜的时候溅油了，把他当盾牌，躲在他身后！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 969548}, {"id": 177665, "content": "老是说我傻……", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 967208}, {"id": 177921, "content": "少吃点", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685190}, {"id": 178177, "content": "拉她的内衣肩带", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1243211}, {"id": 177666, "content": "家里没人的时候，爸爸永远叫我屁孩", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 391759}, {"id": 177922, "content": "不知疲倦的苦口婆心┐(￣ー￣)┌", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 282749}, {"id": 177923, "content": "爱一个人，你会发现你也不知道为啥会爱她，只会满脑子都是她，每时每刻都想她，几天不见犹如数月未见。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 967858}, {"id": 177668, "content": "\"我就是你的药\"\n可惜是假药！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591967}, {"id": 177924, "content": "摸头?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 644503}, {"id": 177669, "content": "打王者荣耀带我飞呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 967214}, {"id": 177925, "content": "考研让我跟她考同一个学院同一个专业算么", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 829273}, {"id": 178181, "content": "特别爱一个人就会各种吐槽", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 830113}, {"id": 177670, "content": "我爸总喜欢看着我憨厚的笑，我妈总是担心我这那的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 967217}, {"id": 177926, "content": "666", "image": "img/option/option/20170312192146qoMT9VZLY7AkPvOp", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921957}, {"id": 178182, "content": "转公众号的文章。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 900957}, {"id": 177671, "content": "洗碗", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 925003}, {"id": 177927, "content": "了解，一种超过你自己的了解。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 954921}, {"id": 192775, "content": "嗯～你肯定会喜欢?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1005721}, {"id": 177672, "content": "和朋友不同的城市上大学，寒假一天晚上，我“明早约早饭”“好”", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 867282}, {"id": 177673, "content": "每次放假结束准备回学校，临走前我爸都问我妈“钱给够了吗，多给些”", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 867282}, {"id": 177929, "content": "洗澡的时候嫌胖 吃饭的时候嫌瘦", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914770}, {"id": 177674, "content": "给钱。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924972}, {"id": 177930, "content": "胖了说我，瘦了点赞！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 710978}, {"id": 177675, "content": "冷战时把头像换了，他自己画了一个，情侣头像！哈哈哈哈哈哈哈，我怕笑的太狂！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 929547}, {"id": 177931, "content": "红包最高200那个 你忘了转账了么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922379}, {"id": 177677, "content": "通常爱称为屎屎屁屁之类…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 548230}, {"id": 177933, "content": "叫我过去到他身边的时候 总是像呼唤宠物犬那样叫我过去?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360185}, {"id": 179981, "content": "多吃点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 491880}, {"id": 186893, "content": "好吃的饭菜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 784138}, {"id": 177678, "content": "只对喜欢的人毒舌", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 868322}, {"id": 177934, "content": " Your nearness takes my breath away&all the things i want to say can find no voice& in silence&i can  hope my eyes will speak my heart .\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130839}, {"id": 177679, "content": "你是我的眼", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919031}, {"id": 178959, "content": "心情不好的时候，被怼一下心情就好了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971297}, {"id": 179471, "content": "无论她发什么朋友圈，都点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 299712}, {"id": 179727, "content": "骂她", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972730}, {"id": 177680, "content": "和朋友直接好吃的总想一起吃  一起分享美食 音乐  电影", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 967257}, {"id": 177936, "content": "很细心，总让我很感动，暖男^_^\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 900106}, {"id": 177681, "content": "和男朋友吃薯条，他一个一个给我喂，结果他突然叼着一个我就咬过去了，吻到了(⁄ ⁄•⁄ω⁄•⁄ ⁄)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 966361}, {"id": 177937, "content": "一定要把饭菜吃完 然后就胖下去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 859898}, {"id": 178193, "content": "发我丑照到朋友圈，亲妈，配字，闺女真好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940404}, {"id": 177682, "content": "my darling truns into poetry at night", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671447}, {"id": 177938, "content": "我爸打电话给我：跟你说个事情。（然后就停顿）我就知道我妈也在家（他家打电话从来都是放免提）。然后回答我爸：我知道了。挂了电话立刻淘宝给他家猫咪买猫粮", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 644807}, {"id": 177683, "content": "把她衣服上的帽子扣在她头上", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 740808}, {"id": 177939, "content": "你喜欢就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 967862}, {"id": 178195, "content": "我妈永远只会盯着我的屁股说：你屁股真大，快去减肥。其他地方通通无视", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193260}, {"id": 178451, "content": "因为我妈和我希望属猪，所以从小到大，她都喊我“猪儿”，这是一个有魔性的叫法。然后她身边的朋友也这么叫我了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 941850}, {"id": 183315, "content": "说微信红包不能超过200的同学，凡事不要说得太绝对哦。春节期间红包金额是会提高到2000，情人节微信红包也推出过520红包，也有可能是爸妈微信转账2000，只不过那位同学口误了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981086}, {"id": 177684, "content": "我想和你一起在清晨醒来。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 945913}]}